Template: tt-local-generator/hf-token
Type: password
Default:
Description: HuggingFace access token (optional for Mochi-1-preview)
 The Mochi-1-preview model (~20 GB) is publicly available on HuggingFace.
 .
 A HuggingFace token can be provided to avoid API rate limits during
 download. Leave blank to download anonymously.
 .
 Your token is used once and immediately discarded — it is not stored by
 this package.
